HEADWORD: Severally
<hw>Sev"er*al*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Separately; distinctly;
apart from others; individually.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>There must be an auditor to check and revise each
<qex>severally</qex> by itself.</q> <rj><qau>De Quincey.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

